LabelList.Name: Challenge Title
LabelList.Description: 8-10 word title identifying a systemic issue from multiple complaints

LabelList.Name: Challenge Description
LabelList.Description: 1–2 sentences describing the recurring issue and its high-level impact

LabelList.Name: Challenge Overview
LabelList.Description: A short paragraph summarizing the challenge’s strategic and operational implications, including key locations and time spans

LabelList.Name: Challenge Cause
LabelList.Description: Root cause analysis of the systemic issue

LabelList.Name: Challenge Type
LabelList.Description: Type of challenge (technical, operational, customer service, policy/regulatory, etc.)

LabelList.Name: Challenge Completeness Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 evaluating whether all required fields are filled with meaningful content

LabelList.Name: Challenge Completeness Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the completeness score

LabelList.Name: Challenge Problem Coverage Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 assessing whether the challenge addresses ALL the problem statements it should cover

LabelList.Name: Challenge Problem Coverage Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the problem coverage score

LabelList.Name: Challenge Data Accuracy Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 evaluating whether dates, locations, and metrics in the challenge are accurate according to the report

LabelList.Name: Challenge Data Accuracy Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the data accuracy score

LabelList.Name: Challenge Specificity Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 assessing whether the challenge contains concrete details rather than vague statements

LabelList.Name: Challenge Specificity Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the specificity score

LabelList.Name: Challenge Overall Score
LabelList.Description: Overall score from 0-10 based on the average of all criteria scores

LabelList.Name: Challenge Overall Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Summary explanation for the overall score

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Title
LabelList.Description: Short, clear title for the recommended action plan

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Description
LabelList.Description: A concise summary of the recommendation, elaborating on its purpose and key aspects. Should be around two to three lines.

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Action Plan
LabelList.Description: 1–2 paragraphs or bullet points detailing proposed solution steps

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Expected Outcome
LabelList.Description: Brief summary of anticipated benefits or improvements

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Required Stakeholders
LabelList.Description: List of key internal and external parties involved

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Risk Level
LabelList.Description: High/Medium/Low, describing the risk if not addressed quickly

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Execution Timeline
LabelList.Description: Suggested timeframe for implementation (immediate, short-term, long-term)

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Business Owner
LabelList.Description: The DEWA division that should take ownership and lead the implementation of this recommendation. Select from the provided divisions.

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Relevance Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 evaluating how well the recommendation addresses the related challenge

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Relevance Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the relevance score

LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the actionability score

LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the feasibility score

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Specificity Score
LabelList.Description: Score from 0-10 assessing whether the recommendation contains detailed rather than vague guidance

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Specificity Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the specificity score

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Stakeholder Clarity Score

LabelList.Name: Recommendation Stakeholder Clarity Reasoning
LabelList.Description: Detailed explanation for the stakeholder clarity score
